 Australia, quickly achieved internet fame, but not necessarily for Olympic-level skill.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0217102578087506e-15, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 1106, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9064417429644723, \"rank\": 0.09101592170658848, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1123, \"end\": 1129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.254086295459292e-39, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999998731818858, \"rank\": 1.2667708649932593e-07, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 1169, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999989308076951, \"rank\": 5.626171817108288e-07, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 36-year-old professor\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"internet fame\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic-level skill\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competing against some b-girls half her age, she was swept out of the round-robin stage without earning a single point, and her unconventional moves landed flat while failing to match the skill level of her foes.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some b-girls\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"the round-robin stage\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"a single point\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"her unconventional moves\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"the skill level\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"her foes\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At one point, Gunn raised one leg while standing and leaned back with her arms bent toward her ears.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1485, \"end\": 1489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9064417429644723, \"rank\": 0.09101592170658848, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"one leg\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"her arms\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"her ears\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At another, while laying on her side, she reached for her toes, flipped over and did it again in a move dubbed \\\"the kangaroo.\\\"\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"her side\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"her toes\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"a move\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"the kangaroo\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn has a Ph.D. in cultural studies, and her LinkedIn page notes she is \\\"interested in the cultural politics of breaking.\\\"\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9064417429644723, \"rank\": 0.09101592170658848, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Ph.D.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural studies\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"the cultural politics\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was never going to beat these girls on what they do best - their power moves,\\\" said Gunn.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1912, \"end\": 1916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9064417429644723, \"rank\": 0.09101592170658848, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these girls\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"their power moves\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What I bring is creativity.\\\"\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clips of her routine have gone viral on TikTok and elsewhere, and many cringed at her moves platformed on the Olympic stage as a representation of hip-hop and breaking culture.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 1995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.997849529693242e-54, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clips\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"her moves\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"a representation\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking culture\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's almost like they are mocking the genre,\\\" wrote one user on X.\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the genre\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2171}, {\"ngram\": \"one user\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2188}, {\"ngram\": \"X.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many Black viewers, in particular, called out Lithuania's silver medalist b-girl Nicka, (legally named Dominika Banevi\\u010d) for donning a durag during each of her battles.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2242, \"end\": 2251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999829243031848, \"rank\": 1.7075972842894687e-05, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many Black viewers\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"Dominika Banevi\\u010d\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"a durag\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"her battles\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Durags, once worn by enslaved Africans to tie up their hair for work, are still worn by Black people to protect and style their hair.\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2386, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slavery_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.986297622028401, \"rank\": 0.01389244118301161, \"text\": \"enslaved Africans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slavery_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slavery_in_the_United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Durags\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2371}, {\"ngram\": \"their hair\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2433}, {\"ngram\": \"Black people\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"their hair\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They became a fashionable symbol of Black pride in the 1960s and 1970s and, in the 1990s and early 2000s, also became a popular element of hip-hop style.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fashionable symbol\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"Black pride\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2546}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1960s\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"1970s\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1990s\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2587}, {\"ngram\": \"early 2000s\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2603}, {\"ngram\": \"a popular element\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2634}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop style\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when worn by those who are not Black, durags can be seen as cultural appropriation.\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2740, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"durags\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2701}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural appropriation\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Banevi\\u010d is white.\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Banevi\\u010d\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Actor Kevin Fredericks responded on Instagram to Banevi\\u010d donning the headwear by saying it looked \\\"weird to see somebody who does not need it for protective style or waves to be rocking the durag.\\\"\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2796, \"end\": 2805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.612699656992916e-39, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Actor Kevin Fredericks\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"Banevi\\u010d\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"the headwear\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2880}, {\"ngram\": \"protective style\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2931}, {\"ngram\": \"the durag\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 17-year-old breaker ultimately won the silver medal after losing in the final to Japan's b-girl Ami (Ami Yuasa).\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 3075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3044, \"end\": 3049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9920805457620799, \"rank\": 0.005037383585827677, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 17-year-old breaker\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver medal\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3014}, {\"ngram\": \"Ami Yuasa\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For her part, Banevi\\u010d has credited the breakers from the 1970s in the Bronx - the OGs - or \\\"original gangsters\\\" in hip-hop who created the dance - for her own success and breaking style.\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3147, \"end\": 3152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bronx\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9224223337644754e-14, \"text\": \"Bronx\", \"types\": [\"Q4